---
---
<section id="contacto" class="section">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="info">
      <span class="label">Contacto</span>
      <h2>¿Listo para empezar?<br>Hablemos.</h2>
      <p class="sub">Cuéntanos de tu proyecto y te respondemos en menos de 24 horas con una propuesta concreta.</p>
      <div class="datos">
        <div class="dato"><label>Email</label><p>contacto@limondigital.cl</p></div>
        <div class="dato"><label>WhatsApp</label><p>+56 9 4747 2145</p></div>
        <div class="dato"><label>Ubicación</label><p>Valparaíso, Chile · 100% remoto</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <form class="form" name="contacto-landing-pro" method="POST" data-netlify="true" data-netlify-honeypot="bot-field" netlify>
      <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contacto" />
      <input type="hidden" name="bot-field" style="display:none" />
      <div class="row">
        <input class="input" type="text" name="nombre" placeholder="Nombre" />
        <input class="input" type="text" name="empresa" placeholder="Empresa" />
      </div>
      <input class="input" type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email" />
      <input class="input" type="text" name="necesidad" placeholder="¿Qué necesitas?" />
      <textarea class="input" name="mensaje" placeholder="Cuéntanos más sobre tu proyecto..."></textarea>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-disabled" disabled>Formulario de demo — no funcional</button>
      <a href="https://limondigital.cl/precios" target="_blank" class="btn-cta">Ver planes y precios →</a>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section { padding: 80px 48px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
  .inner { max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: start; }
  .label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--limon); display: block; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 38px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -1.2px; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .sub { font-size: 15px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 36px; }
  .datos { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }
  .dato label { display: block; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--limon); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .dato p { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
  .form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
  .row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; }
  .input { background: #1a1a1a; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px; color: var(--white); font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 13px; outline: none; transition: border-color 0.2s; width: 100%; }
  .input:focus { border-color: var(--limon); }
  .input::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
  textarea.input { resize: none; height: 100px; }
  .btn { background: var(--limon); color: var(--dark); border: none; padding: 14px; border-radius: 6px; font-family: var(--font-body); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; cursor: pointer; transition: opacity 0.2s; width: 100%; }
  .btn:hover { opacity: 0.88; }
  .btn-disabled { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); cursor: not-allowed; opacity: 1; }
  .btn-disabled:hover { opacity: 1; }
  .btn-cta { background: transparent; color: var(--limon); border: 1px solid var(--limon); padding: 14px; border-radius: 6px; font-family: var(--font-body); font-weight: 500; font-size: 15px; text-decoration: none; text-align: center; width: 100%; display: block; transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s; }
  .btn-cta:hover { background: var(--limon); color: var(--dark); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
  .section { padding: 60px 24px; }
  .inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  h2 { font-size: 28px; }
  .row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
